{"data":[{"date":"14:24 05/08","title":"\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Maguire v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU k\u00edch n\u1ed5 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/bom-tan-maguire-van-co-the-duoc-mu-kich-no-o-he-2018.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo Express, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Co-hoi-de-MU-Harry-Maguire-cua-Leicester-la-van-con-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leicester ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Maguire\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho M.U, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, Maguire s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Van Dijk \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/leicester-lam-dieu-nay-de-giu-chan-harry-maguire-172-192395.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leicester mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Maguire</span>. \u1ede b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 (t\u1eeb 50.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n l\u00ean 95.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Maguire qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n Yerry Mina \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Express, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Co-hoi-de-MU-Harry-Maguire-cua-Leicester-la-van-con-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, Maguire l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1t khao nh\u1ea5t. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo cho Everton \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Mourinho v\u1eabn \u01b0u ti\u00ean Maguire, ch\u1ec9 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u00f4ng m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2029","checkdouble":"193770"},{"date":"14:53 05/08","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-paul-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Iniesta, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Pogba trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sport, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Eric Abidal \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ri\u00eang Pogba, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Pogba m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/cuc-nong-pogba-da-chon-xong-so-ao-o-barca-180-193721.html\" target=\"_blank\">s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf Barca</span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o do huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Pogba M.U\" title=\"tien ve Pogba M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/20/andy-cole-khong-danh-gia-cao-paul-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf cho ph\u00e9p. Theo t\u1edd Daily Star, Mino Raiola s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou quan t\u00e2m Pogba, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ph\u00eda M.U \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Barcelona ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i, Pogba s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p M.U \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2028","checkdouble":"193771"},{"date":"15:59 05/08","title":"Real Madrid nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 200 tri\u1ec7u euro thay Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinaphone 2018 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Oman l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP OLYMPIC VI\u1ec6T NAM VS OLYMPIC OMAN</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DgL2cBwfQ7s\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,\u2026 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay hay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai \u0111i, ai \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o SLNA, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ecfng \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1edfi th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea5u Oman, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, link xem HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, link xem HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Truc-tiep-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-ngay-hom-nay,-link-xem-HD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i U23 c\u1ee7a hai n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (tham d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0110TQG) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p \u0110TQG Oman \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m, trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2004.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Oman v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a 14 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Do \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ti\u1ebfn Linh.<br>\r\nU23 Oman: Mukhaini; Harthi, Rashi Al, Shayadi, Sulaman Al, Balushi, Mubarak Al, Saleh Al, Al Hidi, Ali Al, Al Sabhi.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2027","checkdouble":"193772"},{"date":"15:59 05/08","title":"Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d MU l\u00ean 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian cho MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian cho Barca, song h\u1ecd \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb M.U. Mourinho \u0111ang th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Chelsea-muon-mua-Wilfried-Zaha-thay-Willian-voi-gia-sieu-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri t\u1ecf ra t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng Chelsea do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Willian b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 th\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi \u0111\u1ee7 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Theo Daily Mail, M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i cho Willian, theo \u0111\u00f3 Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Zaha l\u00ean 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/zaha-moi-goi-chelsea-172-192605.html\" target=\"_blank\">Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea</span>, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, HLV Roy Hodgson tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Palace kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Zaha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea muon mua Zaha voi gia 75 trieu bang\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Man City \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ef1u sao M.U, song Palace \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i bu\u1ed9c Man xanh ph\u1ea3i chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester. N\u1ebfu Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Zaha, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Palace t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Mirror, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Willian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zaha. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2026","checkdouble":"193773"},{"date":"15:01 05/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 05/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0508.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 05/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi sao Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0508-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m. Mina s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, t\u1ee9c x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 145.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc thu\u1ebf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Valverde t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-pogba-180-193728.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/12/MU-ap-dao-doi-hinh-te-nhat-vong-9-Premier-League-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-pogba-180-193728.html\">HLV Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba?</span><br>\r\nErnesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan t\u00ednh v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u00e0 Barca trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Maguire v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Express, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea7ng anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Man United, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire hay Yerry Mina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ivan Perisic mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0508 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0508-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian-172-193732.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian-172-193732.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian</span><br>\r\nBenfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, theo \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Martial\" title=\"tien dao Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-38,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mua Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial. Ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Bild.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mateo Kovacic, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a M.U, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham b\u00e1n Alderweireld v\u00e0 Rose cho MU n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham b\u00e1n Alderweireld v\u00e0 Rose cho MU, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-va-rose-cho-mu-172-192610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-va-rose-cho-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-san-sang-ban-alderweireld-va-rose-cho-mu-172-192610.html\">Tottenham nh\u1eafn MU: 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng = Alderweireld + Rose</span><br>\r\nTottenham b\u00e1n Alderweireld v\u00e0 Rose cho MU, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sky Sports \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo CalcioMarceto, Paul Pogba t\u1edbi Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o do huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2025","checkdouble":"193774"},{"date":"16:27 05/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Oman 19h30 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-toi-ngay-hom-nay-58.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinaphone 2018 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Oman l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP OLYMPIC VI\u1ec6T NAM VS OLYMPIC OMAN</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DgL2cBwfQ7s\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,\u2026 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay hay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai \u0111i, ai \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o SLNA, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ecfng \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1edfi th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea5u Oman, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, link xem HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, link xem HD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Truc-tiep-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-ngay-hom-nay,-link-xem-HD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i U23 c\u1ee7a hai n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (tham d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0110TQG) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p \u0110TQG Oman \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m, trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2004.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Oman v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a 14 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Do \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ti\u1ebfn Linh.<br>\r\nU23 Oman: Mukhaini; Harthi, Rashi Al, Shayadi, Sulaman Al, Balushi, Mubarak Al, Saleh Al, Al Hidi, Ali Al, Al Sabhi.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2024","checkdouble":"193775"},{"date":"16:22 05/08","title":"HLV Sarri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 n\u1ed9i dung cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/15/them-mot-ngoi-sao-dem-hung-tin-toi-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui-172-193739.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea vs Man City</span> trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. V\u1edbi The Blues, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard chelsea tottenham\" title=\"Eden Hazard chelsea tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/5/3/33C0369800000578-3569894-image-a-86_1462222192444.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Eden Hazard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Hazard, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Hazard n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi sau m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Hazard, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea. B\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u1ec7n mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Hazard, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Hazard r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u1edbi t\u00f4i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea v\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ecbch NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Chelsea x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u00e9m h\u1ecd t\u1edbi 30 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 san l\u1ea5p \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u00fap Chelsea ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t t\u1ed1t l\u00ean. T\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2023","checkdouble":"193776"},{"date":"16:48 05/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/7/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-se-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Timothy Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Daily Mail c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Hertha Berlin theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fosu-Mensah mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Fosu-Mensah ch\u01a1i cho Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 20 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Timothy Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Timothy Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Timothy-Fosu-Mensah-roi-MU-toi-Duc-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fosu-Mensah mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/fosumensah-tu-tin-canh-tranh-vi-tri-o-mu-mua-toi-172-192303.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fosu-Mensah mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</span>, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, t\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Mourinho\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 HLV th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1ecb tr\u00ed duy nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n\".</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Timothy Fosu-Mensah tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fosu-Mensah s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Timothy Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Daily Mail c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Hertha Berlin theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Timothy Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Timothy Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/4-dieu-Mourinho-can-lam-de-MU-khong-roi-vao-tham-hoa-o-dau-mua-giai-moi-201819-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y Fosu-Mensah t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Hertha Berlin d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea9y sao tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 1998 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Fosu-Mensah b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Chris Smalling, Antonio Valencia, Marcos Rojo, Diogo Dalot, Luke Shaw hay Eric Bailly \u0111\u1ec1u d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Victor Lindelof, Phil Jones v\u00e0 Ashley Young ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Mourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Fosu-Mensah, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng lu\u00f4n \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n thay v\u00ec trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2022","checkdouble":"193777"},{"date":"16:52 05/08","title":"Chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao kh\u1ee7ng Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/27/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Aaron Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal, theo Sunday Express \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Aaron Ramsey h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Aaron Ramsey h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Chi-40-trieu-bang,-Chelsea-muon-mua-Aaron-Ramsey-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Arsenal. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ramsey mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao th\u1ee9 2 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal, sau Mesut Ozil (350.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Arsenal d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng m\u00e0 Ramsey \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho anh l\u00ean 150.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Kh\u00fac m\u1eafc \u1edf m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ramsey</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ramsey ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, trong \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t. Sau khi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 xi\u00eau l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Aaron Ramsey h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Aaron Ramsey h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Truoc-tuong-lai-bat-dinh,-Aaron-Ramsey-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Aaron Ramsey</span> c\u1ee7a Arsenal, theo Sunday Express \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 5 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua. C\u00e1c CLB \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Ramsey v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 5 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2021","checkdouble":"193778"},{"date":"17:17 05/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Chelsea vs Man City 21h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-hom-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Man City: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Chelsea Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh Community Shield 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN</h2>\r\n- Man City: De Bruyne v\u00e0 Sterling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n- Chelsea: Hazard, Willian, Courtois kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Fabregas ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n- Theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 3/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Man City ch\u1ec9 thua 3/9 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n- 7 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n- Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh.<br>\r\n- Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 20 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Wembley - ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Tottenham (32), MU (23), Arsenal (21) \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u1edf s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Man City tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs Man City tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/manchester-city-vs-chelsea-community-shield-2018_wqse.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea vs Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T</h2>\r\nT\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean: 8/9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi tr\u1edf l\u00ean. HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<h2>PH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U</h2>\r\nPep Guardiola (HLV Man City): \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n  Maurizio Sarri. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t  tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y hy v\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean\u201d.<br>\r\nMaurizio  Sarri (HLV Chelsea): \u201cChelsea s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh. Man City d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t  m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0  m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay\u201d<br>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a  Opta, d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng  \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 2 CLB t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t cho m\u1ed9t  ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi trung b\u00ecnh 490 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng  cho m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Man xanh b\u1ecf ra cho m\u1ed7i  l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 440 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a  t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League l\u00e0 Liverpool. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi 1,1 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a  l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u0103ng quang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal 1-1 (pen 6-5) Chelsea\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2020","checkdouble":"193779"},{"date":"09:09 05/08","title":"Arsenal kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/emery-xac-nhan-monreal-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Arsenal c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1ea5n n\u1ea1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, Sead Kolasinac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111au ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i. Anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm \u1edf ph\u00fat 70 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Ainsley Maitland-Niles.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ec9 ra Kolasinac s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i trong \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 2 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Arsenal m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef t\u1eeb Nacho Monreal. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/emery-xac-nhan-monreal-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monreal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Man City l\u00fac 22h ng\u00e0y 12/8 t\u1edbi v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Maitland-Niles.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMonreal kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi HLV th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i\u201d, Emery n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u0129 nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed9n sau khi d\u1ef1 World Cup nh\u01b0 Montreal v\u00e0 c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y k\u1ecbp d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Manchester City.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Maitland-Niles th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-muon-gianh-hang-hot-world-cup-voi-arsenal-va-liverpool-172-193730.html\">T\u00e2n binh Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng hot World Cup v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-193727.html\">Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-193727.html\">Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kolasinac-chan-thuong-nghi-10-tuan-172-193693.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 10 tu\u1ea7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-voi-roma-172-192633.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Roma</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2019","checkdouble":"193754"},{"date":"09:45 05/08","title":"Smalling kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ebfm x\u1ec9a \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/smalling-khong-them-dem-xia-den-viec-mu-mua-them-trung-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa n\u00e0y ra \u0111i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric b\u1ecb s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Luka Modric \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid, anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. L\u00ean \u0110T Croatia, Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Modric th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Inter Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/HLV-Lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Modric t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nInter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luciano Spalletti c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Real kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, HLV Julen Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"779\" height=\"357\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/hlv-lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn g\u00ec kh\u00e1c\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cLuka Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng tay r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Modric sau k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau khi Modric tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng xem li\u1ec7u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00eam 15/8) hay kh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Modric s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-co-mua-them-tien-dao-hay-khong-180-193677.html\">Real \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-se-roi-chelsea-cap-ben-real-o-he-2018-172-193672.html\">Courtois s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-hoi-mua-mateo-kovacic-176-193644.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh sao Real v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nong-hlv-real-bat-ngo-che-thibaut-courtois-180-192594.html\">N\u00f3ng: HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u201cch\u00ea\u201d Thibaut Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2018","checkdouble":"193757"},{"date":"09:25 05/08","title":"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/xem-truc-tiep-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-o-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV6 nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 NHM s\u1ebd xem tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua k\u00eanh VTV5 c\u1ee7a \u0110TH Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean VTV6</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDo tr\u00f9ng gi\u1edd v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n n\u1eef VTV Cup 2018 n\u00ean thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV6 nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV5.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Xem-truc-tiep-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-o-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa&nbsp;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV5</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Uzbekistan vs Palestine c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tr\u00ean k\u00eanh n\u00e0y do k\u00eanh VTV6 ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n n\u1eef gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi \u0110T n\u1eef Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i VTV Cup n\u00ean lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV5. Ngo\u00e0i ra, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" target=\"_blank\">Bongda24h </span>c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Oman t\u1ed1i nay, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 4/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 trong khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a VFF. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho t\u1eadp ri\u00eang. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang Seo cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea5u Oman. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi&nbsp;tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3&nbsp;chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\">L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Oman: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?</span><br />\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br />\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2017","checkdouble":"193758"},{"date":"09:47 05/08","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-chi-ra-nguoi-da-cap-tot-nhat-voi-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00f4m 3/8 v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 cho r\u1eb1ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.</h2><h2>HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf h\u00f4m 3/8. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/HLV-Tran-Binh-Su-chi-ra-nguoi-da-cap-tot-nhat-voi-Cong-Phuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"width: 779px;\">\r\n            <table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><em>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o Th\u1ec3 thao V\u0103n h\u00f3a, \u00f4ng S\u1ef1 \u2018g\u1ed7\u2019 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \u201cH\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec y\u00ean t\u00e2m r\u1ed3i. Theo t\u00f4i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t, kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n. Khi g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t th\u00ec anh ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e8, l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00fat h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2u v\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec v\u1edbi Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. Khi c\u1ea7n lui v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u2018tay ngh\u1ec1\u2019 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo khi x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ai bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y, HLV Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111ang c\u00f3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u00ean VTV5. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2016","checkdouble":"193760"},{"date":"10:10 05/08","title":"HLV Real Madrid ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa n\u00e0y ra \u0111i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric b\u1ecb s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Luka Modric \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid, anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. L\u00ean \u0110T Croatia, Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Modric th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Inter Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/HLV-Lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Modric t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nInter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luciano Spalletti c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Real kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, HLV Julen Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"779\" height=\"357\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/hlv-lopetegui-noi-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn g\u00ec kh\u00e1c\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cLuka Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng tay r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Modric sau k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau khi Modric tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng xem li\u1ec7u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00eam 15/8) hay kh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Modric s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-co-mua-them-tien-dao-hay-khong-180-193677.html\">Real \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-se-roi-chelsea-cap-ben-real-o-he-2018-172-193672.html\">Courtois s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-hoi-mua-mateo-kovacic-176-193644.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh sao Real v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nong-hlv-real-bat-ngo-che-thibaut-courtois-180-192594.html\">N\u00f3ng: HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u201cch\u00ea\u201d Thibaut Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2015","checkdouble":"193761"}]}